## MCP Client Configuration

Add to your MCP client config:

```json
{
  "<< project_slug >>": {
<% if language == "python" %>
    "command": "/path/to/<< project_slug >>/.venv/bin/python",
    "args": ["-m", "<< package_name >>.mcp_server"]
<% else %>
    "command": "node",
    "args": ["/path/to/<< project_slug >>/src/mcp-server.js"]
<% endif %>
  }
}
```

## Adding tools

<% if language == "python" %>
Edit `src/<< package_name >>/mcp_server.py` and add new `@mcp.tool()` decorated functions.
<% else %>
Edit `src/mcp-server.js` and add new tool definitions and handlers.
<% endif %>

